* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:01 Page   1
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC5.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC5.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION    DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC5.
     3 AUTHOR.        YHAGO.
     4 INSTALLATION.    FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.    24/05/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 26-May-25 20:01.
     7 SECURITY.    APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICAR.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT    DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION    SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.    IBM-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.    IBM-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT     SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT ARQVENDA ASSIGN TO DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT ARQ-SORT ASSIGN TO DISK.
    20     SELECT RELVENDA ASSIGN TO DISK
    21     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    22
    23 DATA    DIVISION.
    24 FILE    SECTION.
    25 FD ARQVENDA
    26     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    27     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADENT.DAT".
    28 01 REG-CLIENTE.
    29     02 ESTADO-ENT        PIC X(02).
    30     02 NR-VENDEDOR-ENT   PIC 9(05).
    31     02 NOME-VENDEDOR-ENT PIC X(20).
    32     02 VALOR-VENDA-ENT   PIC 9(07)V99.
    33 SD ARQ-SORT.
    34 01 REG-SORT.
    35     02 ESTADO-SORT        PIC X(02).
    36     02 NR-VENDEDOR-SORT   PIC 9(05).
    37     02 NOME-VENDEDOR-SORT PIC X(20).
    38     02 VALOR-VENDA-SORT   PIC 9(07)V99.
    39 FD RELVENDA
    40     LABEL RECORD  OMITTED.
    41 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(80).
    42 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    43     77 FIM-ARQ-ENTRADA  PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    44     77 FIM-ARQ-SAIDA    PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    45     77 CT-LIN           PIC 9(02) VALUE 20.
    46     77 CT-PAG           PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    47     77 ESTADO           PIC X(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    48     77 NR-VENDEDOR      PIC 9(05) VALUE ZEROS.
    49     77 SOMA-VENDEDOR    PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    50     77 SOMA-ESTADO      PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    51     77 SOMA-COMPANHIA   PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    52 01 CAB.
    53     02 FILLER     PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
    54 01 CAB-01.
    55     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
    56     02 FILLER     PIC X(35)
    57         VALUE "VENDAS TOTAIS POR ESTADO - VENDEDOR".
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:01 Page   2
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
    58     02 FILLER     PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    59     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    60     02 VAR-PAG    PIC ZZ9.
    61 01 CAB-ESTADO.
    62     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "ESTADO: ".
    63     02 VAR-ESTADO PIC X(02).
    64 01 CAB-02.
    65     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE "NRO DO VENDEDOR".
    67     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    68     02 FILLER     PIC X(16) VALUE "NOME DO VENDEDOR".
    69     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    70     02 FILLER     PIC X(14) VALUE "VALOR DA VENDA".
    71 01 DETALHE-01.
    72     02 FILLER      PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    73     02 VAR-NUMERO    PIC ZZZZ9.
    74     02 FILLER      PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    75     02 VAR-NOME    PIC X(20).
    76     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    77     02 VAR-VALOR-01  PIC ZZZZZZ9,99.
    78 01 DETALHE-02.
    79     02 FILLER     PIC X(60) VALUE SPACES.
    80     02 VAR-VALOR-02  PIC ZZZZZZ9,99.
    81 01 RODAPE-VENDEDOR.
    82     02 FILLER     PIC X(39) VALUE SPACES.
    83     02 FILLER     PIC X(19) VALUE "TOTAL DO VENDEDOR: ".
    84     02 VAR-VALOR-VENDEDOR  PIC ZZZZZZZZ9,99.
    85 01 RODAPE-ESTADO.
    86     02 FILLER     PIC X(42) VALUE SPACES.
    87     02 FILLER     PIC X(17) VALUE "TOTAL DO ESTADO: ".
    88     02 VAR-VALOR-ESTADO  PIC ZZZZZZZZ9,99.
    89 01 RODAPE-COMPANHIA.
    90     02 FILLER     PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
    91     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE "TOTAL DA COMPANHIA: ".
    92     02 VAR-VALOR-COMPANHIA  PIC ZZZZZZZZ9,99.
    93 PROCEDURE    DIVISION.
    94 PGM-EX05.
    95 SORT    ARQ-SORT
    96         ON ASCENDING KEY ESTADO-SORT
    97         ON ASCENDING KEY NR-VENDEDOR-SORT
    98         USING ARQVENDA
    99         OUTPUT PROCEDURE ROT-RELATORIO.
   100 STOP    RUN.
   101
   102 ROT-RELATORIO SECTION.
   103     PERFORM INICIO-SAIDA.
   104     PERFORM PRINCIPAL-SAIDA
   105             UNTIL FIM-ARQ-SAIDA EQUAL "SIM".
   106     PERFORM FIM-SAIDA.
   107
   108 INICIO-SAIDA SECTION.
   109     OPEN OUTPUT RELVENDA.
   110     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   111
   112 LEITURA-SAIDA SECTION.
   113     RETURN ARQ-SORT INTO REG-SORT
   114      AT END
   115      PERFORM RODAPE
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:01 Page   3
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
   116      MOVE 'SIM' TO FIM-ARQ-SAIDA.
   117
   118 PRINCIPAL-SAIDA SECTION.
   119     PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA.
   120     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   121
   122 GRAVACAO-SAIDA SECTION.
   123     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 19
   124         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   125     END-IF.
   126     IF NOT(ESTADO-SORT = ESTADO)
   127          PERFORM CABECALHO-02
   128     END-IF.
   129     MOVE ESTADO-SORT TO ESTADO.
   130     PERFORM DETALHES.
   131 CABECALHO-01   SECTION.
   132     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   133     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   134     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   135     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
   136     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   137     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   138     MOVE 1  TO CT-LIN.
   139 CABECALHO-02 SECTION.
   140     MOVE ESTADO-SORT TO VAR-ESTADO.
   141     MOVE SOMA-VENDEDOR TO VAR-VALOR-VENDEDOR.
   142     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-VENDEDOR AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   143     MOVE ZEROS TO SOMA-VENDEDOR.
   144     IF NOT(SOMA-ESTADO = ZEROS)
   145         MOVE SOMA-ESTADO TO VAR-VALOR-ESTADO
   146         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   147         MOVE ZEROES TO SOMA-ESTADO
   148     END-IF.
   149     IF CT-LIN = 1
   150         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   151         ADD 3         TO CT-LIN
   152     ELSE
   153         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   154         ADD 4         TO CT-LIN
   155     END-IF.
   156     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   157 DETALHES SECTION.
   158     IF NOT(NR-VENDEDOR-SORT = NR-VENDEDOR)
   159         IF NOT(SOMA-VENDEDOR = ZEROS)
   160             MOVE SOMA-VENDEDOR TO VAR-VALOR-VENDEDOR
   161             WRITE REG-ATR
   162             FROM RODAPE-VENDEDOR AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   163         END-IF
   164         MOVE NR-VENDEDOR-SORT TO NR-VENDEDOR
   165         MOVE NR-VENDEDOR-SORT TO VAR-NUMERO
   166         MOVE NOME-VENDEDOR-SORT TO VAR-NOME
   167         MOVE VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO VAR-VALOR-01
   168         WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE-01 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   169         MOVE VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-VENDEDOR
   170         ADD VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-ESTADO
   171         ADD VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-COMPANHIA
   172         ADD 2        TO CT-LIN
   173     ELSE
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:01 Page   4
*                                      EXERC5.CBL
   174         MOVE VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO VAR-VALOR-02
   175         WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE-02 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   176         ADD VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-VENDEDOR
   177         ADD VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-ESTADO
   178         ADD VALOR-VENDA-SORT TO SOMA-COMPANHIA
   179         ADD 1         TO CT-LIN
   180     END-IF.
   181
   182 RODAPE SECTION.
   183     MOVE SOMA-VENDEDOR TO VAR-VALOR-VENDEDOR.
   184     MOVE SOMA-ESTADO TO VAR-VALOR-ESTADO.
   185     MOVE SOMA-COMPANHIA TO VAR-VALOR-COMPANHIA.
   186     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-VENDEDOR AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   187     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   188     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-COMPANHIA AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   189
   190 FIM-SAIDA SECTION.
   191     CLOSE RELVENDA.
